{"tid":380623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★中環摩天輪昨起突停業","createTime":"2017-08-30T09:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T16:03:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdf5a4827db2258df83bf84bee4e46e6b798375","tid":380623,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"位於中環海濱長廊的「香港摩天輪」昨日(29日)起突然停業，未知是否與用地易手有關。發展局早前公布，有關用地已易手，預計下月轉交新營辦者，當時未有透露確實交接日及情況，但昨日終「無聲無息」地停業，不少人吃閉門羹。現有營辨者發言人表示，暫時未有消息可公布。<br />\n<br />\n發展局早前表示，「香港摩天輪」逾7000平方米用地的短期租約今年下半年屆滿，經招標再批出為期3年的租約，由公司The Entertainment Corporation Limited以月租150萬港元中標，3年後按季續租。根據新合約，新營者須繼續經營摩天輪，但是否沿用上一手的摩天輪，抑或拆卸重建，以及何時起正式復辦，則未有定案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bkn-20170830164851902-0830_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fbkn-20170830164851902-0830_00822_001.html&d=FpXqscEZCIuu4ZQJylopv6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c5d3a724\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bkn-20170830164851902-0830_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"72aefcc45f5b076e92405c2c1bb6063e735ffa84","tid":380623,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830164851902-0830_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170830170313\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830164851902-0830_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170830170313&h=9b95d470&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5b2a100330df6ed7abd340b1f8d31554497cb56","tid":380623,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bad23069f53142ae675dc178